<emphasis bold="true" box="[1021,1042,1861,1887]" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">A</emphasis>
. Head, lateral view. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1291,1311,1862,1888]" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">B</emphasis>
